text: The Executable class performs the execution part of an agent. If it is a Collection agent, it routes data into the workflow, and if it is a Processing or Forwarding agent, it consumes data from the previous agent in the workflow. There are two branches for agent executables, one for batch and one for real-time workflows. The different types will be explained separately. They both share the same abstract class DRAgent .
